{"tid":435545,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉小麗: 傾向不參與首輪九西補選","createTime":"2017-10-14T11:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T01:49:46.000Z","uid":134071,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ab5c47642cf6df75d58691fbe382d666109cc7","tid":435545,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171014/57329657\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171014%2F57329657&d=qhykyEhMnRht1cruuPfc5ePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=da0316a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171014%2F57329657&h=fb4b3058\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171014/57329657</a><br />\n<br />\n 【九西補選】劉小麗傾向不參與 冀民主派以最佳陣容奪回議席<br />\n\t<br />\n45,134<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 1014 10:00<br />\n<br />\n九龍西和新界東立法會補選將於明年3月11日，同樣被取消議員資格的小麗民主教室劉小麗向部分傳媒透露她就補選的立場。<br />\n<br />\n劉小麗指，自己傾向不參選首次補選，認為民主派應用最好的陣容奪回議席。<br />\n<br />\n以下是她的全文：<br />\n<br />\n「就3.11補選的安排，早前我曾說過積極考慮參選，當時是建基於青年新政表示無意參選。最近青政傳出有機會派人參選，不少記者朋友因此追問我的意向是否有變。<br />\n<br />\n這次補選的背景是源於一次無理釋法，及其後荒謬地褫奪議員資格的政治打壓。因此，民主派及其支持者當前最重要的是在這兩次相關的補選中，力抗DQ，以對抗威權政府的政治壓逼，將被無理剝奪的議席回復。<br />\n<br />\n故此我認為，在第一輪的補選中，青政作為首輪被DQ者，若青政派人參選，我傾向不參選。<br />\n<br />\n我想強調，從大局出發，當前最重要的問題，是民主陣營要拚盡全力奪回中共竊奪的議席，因此民主陣營能否以最好的陣容、每區統一出戰，攸關重要，也是我們對支持民主的市民應該做到的事。所以我希望青年新政能盡快向民主陣營的支持者披露其選派名單，以讓民主陣營的支持者及政團早日商議，凝聚共識。把議席重奪，才可真正做到抗DQ，拒絕政治打壓。」"},{"pid":"e70021fd3eb41b3207149da2a5488e92e127eef2","tid":435545,"uid":102096,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:16:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8087af99ce038bcac7b48ddf7ec9be71a5111902","tid":435545,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:20:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撚仲有人投你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw捐左幾多糧出嚟?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢D票源唔係高登仔連登仔<br />\n<br />\n果時成班高登仔狂轟佢, 話唔投佢, 結果...."},{"pid":"89109dd925c32bd431ef250057a3eab3b92e804e","tid":435545,"uid":95096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:27:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名睇宣布左放棄社運既熱狗出黎撼其他人"},{"pid":"b3c662c91d995bc2c16315ad888aec58773af255","tid":435545,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:28:25.000Z","msg":"閘都入唔到啦"},{"pid":"eb5af40956d2ec80fd79738d02de4f9ee99d271a","tid":435545,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:32:28.000Z","msg":"準備含淚投入到閘民主黨"},{"pid":"36a1c43c33ece1471d5ca52d54013c390e8f9e5a","tid":435545,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:33:11.000Z","msg":"馮檢基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1586ec6f480c342c84eb96e78799fdc6bc3facbc","tid":435545,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:38:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>馮檢基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n何啟明退黨出嚟選啦仆街<br />\n上次選舉論壇佢仲sharp過鄺囝"},{"pid":"e272a6da80c3b9788c58329d9bb26cf6ac15010c","tid":435545,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T14:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2f4e095878dee4f26fd3d843b85bbdd35557e4","tid":435545,"uid":59494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T14:42:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>馮檢基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n何啟明退黨出嚟選啦仆街<br />\n上次選舉論壇佢仲sharp過鄺囝</blockquote><br />\n民協玩關愛座制度 畀馮檢基死霸爛霸都唔推